{"id":320536,"type":4,"name":"Pathfinder: Wrath of the Righteous","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/0b/08/320536_GlI1g.jpg","rating":{"total":28,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":1,"6":1,"7":5,"8":11,"9":9,"10":1},"score":8},"summary":"　　由备受好评的《开拓者：拥王者》的制作团队所推出的全新RPG史诗巨作。\r\n　　循着这段旅程，你将前往世界之伤，直面一道连通深渊界的位面裂隙，感受席卷这片土地的恐惧。一个多世纪以来，周边国家为击退敌军而英勇奋战，但始终收效甚微。如今，你有机会结束这场纷争，但救世之路绝不会一帆风顺。\r\n　　你会成为神圣的天使、狂暴的恶魔、强大的巫妖、狡诈的诡计大师、超然的御衡者、桀骜的灵使、睿智的金龙、吞噬一切的虫群行者，或是保留肉体凡身、披荆斩棘、成为当世传奇？\r\n　　率领你的军队，挑战强大的恶魔领主，探索善与恶的本质，了解力量的真正代价，并超凡飞升，成为能够行凡人所不能之事的神话英雄，彻底改变你和整个世界的命运。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>开拓者：正义之怒</li><li><span>开发: </span><a href=\"/person/43745\">Owlcat Games</a></li><li><span>发行: </span><a href=\"/person/43745\">Owlcat Games</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>正义生气</li><li><span>平台: </span>PC</li><li><span>游戏类型: </span>CRPG</li><li><span>游戏引擎: </span>Unity</li><li><span>游玩人数: </span>1人</li><li><span>发行日期: </span>2021年9月2日</li><li><span>售价: </span>¥188</li><li><span>官方网站: </span>https://wrath.owlcatgames.com/</li><li><span>Kickstarter: </span>https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/owlcatgames/pathfinder-wrath-of-the-righteous/comments</li>","collection":{"wish":31,"collect":21,"doing":17,"on_hold":2,"dropped":3},"tags":[{"name":"PC","count":12},{"name":"CRPG","count":12},{"name":"2021","count":7},{"name":"RPG","count":6},{"name":"STEAM","count":5},{"name":"欧美系","count":3},{"name":"2022","count":2},{"name":"169","count":1},{"name":"2022下","count":1},{"name":"ARPG","count":1},{"name":"galgame","count":1}],"crt":[{"id":100644,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/bd/49/100644_crt_s7xw1.jpg","name":"席拉","desc":"主角"},{"id":100645,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/5e/60/100645_crt_U1A4l.jpg","name":"柯米丽雅","desc":"主角"},{"id":100647,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/8a/1f/100647_crt_yAeE8.jpg","name":"兰恩","desc":"主角"},{"id":100649,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/ea/99/100649_crt_Xgk40.jpg","name":"沃尔吉夫·杰夫托","desc":"主角"},{"id":100650,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/76/ee/100650_crt_85K85.jpg","name":"小